{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述孙小红与李寻欢初遇的过程。孙小红是个活泼聪慧的姑娘，主动找李寻欢斗酒，并以问答作为拼酒规则。在拼酒过程中，她接连透露惊人消息：那封引李寻欢现身的信是林仙儿写的，目的是诱杀李寻欢；阿飞虽然仍与林仙儿在一起，但对她暗中所做之事一无所知；而最想杀李寻欢的人正是上官金虹。这些消息让李寻欢深感震惊，也揭示了林仙儿与上官金虹的阴谋。孙小红还透露自己是说书老人孙白发的孙女，祖孙二人相依为命。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这是你错过杀他的第一次机会，你还要不要我再说第二次？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不说也罢。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "别人都说李寻欢是个真正的男人，想不到原来也有些娘娘腔。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你既然没话说，为什么不咳嗽呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "姑娘目光如炬，想必也是位高人，我倒失敬了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你少捧我，我还没有你肩膀那么高，怎么能算是高人？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道你一向不愿自夸自赞，总是替别人吹嘘，这是你的好处，却也正是你的毛病，一个人既然活着，就不能太委屈自己。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "姑娘……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我既不姓'姑'，也不叫做'娘'，你为什么总是叫我姑娘？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我姓孙，叫孙小红，可不是上官金虹那个'虹'，而是红黄蓝白那个'红'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "在下李……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你的名字我早就知道了，而且早就想找你斗一斗！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "斗什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我自然不会找你斗武功，若论武功，我再练一百年也比不上你，我是想找你斗酒的，我只要听说有人酒量比我好，心里就不服气。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我知道喝酒的人都有这毛病，却想不到你也有同病。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只不过我现在找你斗酒，未免占了你的便宜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你方才和人拼过命，体力自然差些，酒量也未免要打个折扣，喝酒也和比武一样，天时地利人和，这三样是一样也差不得的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "就凭你这一句话，已不愧为酒中高手，能与你这样的高手斗酒，醉亦无憾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么……我既已占了天时，就不能再占地利，这地方就由你来选吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "既是如此，请随我来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "那么你爷爷现在为何没有在你身边呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我爷爷到城外接人去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "小李飞刀，例不虚发，你这手飞刀是怎么练出来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "听说你有个好朋友叫'阿飞'，他出手之快，也和你差不多，但现在他忽然失踪了，你知不知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你也失踪了两年，江湖中谁也想不到你原来一直躲在孙驼子的小店里，你为什么要躲在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在你行藏既露，以后来找你的人一定不少，你是不是还打算留在这里？如果你想走，又要去哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "梅花盗究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他已有两年未露面，是不是已被人除去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他是被谁除去的？是不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在我们可以开始拼酒了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，你说我们该如何拼法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "拼酒难道还有许多种方法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "当然了，你不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我只知道一种方法，那就是大家都把酒喝到肚子里去，谁喝的酒先在肚子里造反，谁就输了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "如此看来，你喝酒的学问还是不够。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "拼酒有文拼，有武拼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "文拼是如何拼法？武拼又是如何拼法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你刚刚说的法子，就是武拼，那简直是牛饮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "牛饮？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "大家直着脖子，把酒拼命往嘴里倒，不是牛饮是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不把酒往嘴里倒，难道往耳朵里倒？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你要真能用耳朵喝酒，我倒真比不过你，只好算你赢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "用耳朵喝酒太慢，我可没那么斯文。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我一个女孩子，怎么能跟你武拼？但文拼也有许多种，你可以随便选一种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "有哪几种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有猜拳行令，击鼓传花，但这些法子都太俗气，像我们这种人拼酒，自然不能用这么俗气的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "如此说来，还剩下几种法子来让我选呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只剩下一种法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "虽然只剩下一种法子，但这种法子不但最新奇，也最有趣，就算有一万种法子，你也一定会选这种的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "酒已在桌，我只想快点喝下去，用什么法子都无妨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你听着，这法子其实也简单得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我问你一句话，你若能回答，就算你赢了，我就得喝一大杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我若答不出，就算输了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你就算回答不出，也不算输，直到我将自己问的这问题回答出来，你才算输。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说这法子公平不公平？好不好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我若输了，就轮到我来问你了，是吗？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不对，赢的人可以一直问下去，直到输为止。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你若一直问我些你的私人琐事，我岂非要一直输到底？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我当然不能问你那些话，我若问你，我母亲是谁，我兄弟有几人，我有几岁……你当然不知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "那么，你准备问些什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只要拼酒一开始，你就可以听到我要问些什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我已在准备输了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你听着，我现在就开始问你第一句话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知不知道那封信是谁写的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我不知道……你难道知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我若不知道，就不会问你了，写那封信的人就是……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就是林仙儿！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你怎么知道是她？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在还未轮到你问我，先喝了这杯酒再说吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你可知道阿飞现在的情况？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他虽然还是和林仙儿在一起，但林仙儿做的事，他却完全被蒙在鼓里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他……他现在何处？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你怎么如此性急，等你赢了时再问也不迟呀？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你可知道林仙儿为何要写那封信？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为她知道只要有人想对龙夫人林诗音不利，你就一定会挺身而出的，她要诱你现身，再找人杀你！因为她一直将你当做最大的对头，最怕的是你，最恨的也是你，你若不死，她就不敢出头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你可知道第一个要杀你的人是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "要杀我的人太多了，又岂非一个？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但能杀得了你的人却也许只有两三个，第一个就是上官金虹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他现在来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    }
